<DOCNO> LA041494-0068 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 032006 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
April 14, 1994, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
South Bay; Part J; Page 3 
