<BYLINE>
<P>
By CARLOS V. LOZANO 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Former President Gerald Ford will host a fund-raising barbecue dinner tonight 
for Brooks Firestone, a candidate for the 35th Assembly District seat that 
includes portions of western Ventura County. 
</P>
<P>
 "I am delighted to give Brooks a hand," Ford said in a statement."He's a 
straight-talker and he's dedicated to fighting crime." 
</P>
<P>
 Firestone, who is uncontested in the Republican primary in June, said he was 
honored by Ford's endorsement. He said the two are longtime friends. 
</P>
<P>
 The fund-raising event will be held on the grounds of the Firestone winery in 
the Santa Ynez Valley. 
</P>
<P>
