winner of the Democratic primary in November. Competing for the Democratic 
nomination are Bob Ream, a former aide to state Sen. Gary Hart (D-Santa 
Barbara), and Mindy Lorenz, an art history instructor at Cal State Northridge. 
</P>
<P>
 The 35th Assembly District encompasses Ventura, Santa Paula, Ojai and most of 
Santa Barbara County. The seat is now held by Assemblyman Jack O'Connell 
(D-Carpinteria), who is running for Hart's seat in the state Senate. 
</P>
