<HEADLINE>
<P>
3 POST OFFICES TO STAY OPEN FOR TAX FILING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Three San Gabriel Valley post offices will be open until midnight Friday to 
accommodate last-minute income tax filers. They are the Pasadena main office, 
600 Lincoln Ave.; the Arcadia main office, 41 Wheeler Ave., and the Industry 
post office, 15421 Gale Ave. 
</P>
<P>
 The post offices will be selling stamps and collecting and postmarking all 
returns deposited by midnight. 
</P>
