 The public is invited to participate in three grass volleyball tournaments at 
Azusa Pacific University. Pairs competition in men's A, men's B, women's A and 
co-ed divisions will are scheduled for Friday, May 7 and June 16. The entry fee 
is $15 a team in advance, $17 on the day of the tournament. Information: (818) 
812-3024. GARY KLEIN 
