 La Habra 8, Troy 4 -- Jeremy Payne's three-run double in the fifth inning 
helped secure the lead for La Habra (5-8, 1-5). Aaron Yessian had three hits 
and two RBIs, and Donny Cisneros had three hits and three runs scored. 
</P>
<P>
 Freshman Jeremy Weinberg earned his second victory, pitching 4 2/3 innings for 
La Habra. 
</P>
