said Wednesday after signing a two-year, $1.8-million contract with the 
Washington Redskins. 
</P>
<P>
 Ellard leads the Rams in receptions (593) and receiving yards (9,761) in his 
11 seasons. He will receive an $800,000 signing bonus from the Redskins and 
