<HEADLINE>
<P>
NIBBLES AND BITS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
Compiled by Ken Williams 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Orange County Chamber Orchestra raised $3,000 with a benefit concert and 
dinner Saturday in Costa Mesa. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA041494-0300 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 032238 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
April 14, 1994, Thursday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
