<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY EARNINGS: ICU POSTS FIRST-QUARTER PROFIT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 ICU Medical Inc., an Irvine maker of medical connectors, reported net income 
of $1.09 million for the first quarter, compared to earnings of $1.13 million 
for the same period a year earlier. Revenue rose 43% to $4.18 million from 
$2.91 million. 
</P>
