<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY EARNINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Renaissance Golf Products Inc.: The Huntington Beach company, which does 
business as Fila Golf, reported a 1993 loss of $3.3 million, or 97 cents a 
share.That compared to a loss of $880,000, or 30 cents a share, for the 
previous 12 months. Annual revenue was $3 million, compared to $3.7 million for 
1992. The company attributed the 1993 results to its lack of operating capital 
caused by a delay in its initial public stock offering, which was completed in 
November. 
</P>
